text: Barbara Bellenberg (born 19 July 1993) is a German female badminton player. == Achievements == === BWF Grand Prix (1 title) === The BWF Grand Prix has two level such as Grand Prix and Grand Prix Gold. It is a series of badminton tournaments, sanctioned by Badminton World Federation (BWF) since 2007.
